deck: Sadik was a ruthless criminal whose black suit became impenetrable thanks to a regenerative bath.
description:
Sadik is the crime lord. Nobody knows his mysterious origins. He is feared worldwide for his almost supernatural powers. He is cruel and elusive . Sadik is called the lord of crime but his victims are in fact criminals of various kinds that sooner or later would have been caught by the law.

His primary enemy isl Eddy Castle.

Sadik's tights are special. Periodic immersion in a mysterious solution makes the fabric indestructible and consequently the wearer becomes invulnerable.
name: Sadik

deck: Part of the wave of Italian comic book characters inspired by Diabolik introduced in the 1960's. Not to be confused with the Italian character Satanik, who was named Demoniak in French comics.
description:
In his first incarnation Demoniak was a scientist turned criminal in black suit, with an exceptional scientific genius but decidedly megalomaniac plans; Demoniak wants to create a super race to dominate the world. Helping Diabolik is his companion Eve. On his trail is the inspector Mant, trying to catch him with the help of a group of telepaths.

In the second volume of Demoniak his alter ego is Alex Gordon, president and majority shareholder of a large research company. His archenemy is Inspector Carter.
name: Demoniak
